Huwag kang maging katawa-tawa.

00:48:43.442 --> 00:48:45.402
Malamang binili mo na siya nang maaga.

00:48:49.448 --> 00:48:51.283
Kung ginawa ko,

00:48:52.117 --> 00:48:53.618
Dapat natutunan ko 'yan sa'yo.

00:48:54.745 --> 00:48:57.497
"Walang tao sa mundong ito
na walang kahinaan."

00:48:58.331 --> 00:49:00.625
"Kung mayroon mang ganoong tao,

00:49:01.918 --> 00:49:04.629
magtanim ng kahinaan."

00:49:13.764 --> 00:49:15.098
Humanga ako.

00:49:17.809 --> 00:49:18.643
Sige.

00:49:19.811 --> 00:49:23.273
Panoorin ko
pa nang kaunti ang laro mong pambata.

00:49:39.164 --> 00:49:41.625
TRANSKRIPT

