Pwede kang umupo rito kung gusto mo.
Kakausapin ko si Oh Jung-in--

00:51:44.289 --> 00:51:45.290
Ayos lang.

00:51:46.708 --> 00:51:48.543
Desisyon ng nakararami,

00:51:49.169 --> 00:51:50.337
kaya dapat ko itong sundin.

00:51:52.172 --> 00:51:53.089
Jun-u.

00:51:53.173 --> 00:51:55.675
Gagawin ko ang trabaho ko bilang bahagi ng team.

00:51:56.468 --> 00:51:58.345
Gawin mo rin ang trabaho mo, Ginoong Kang.

00:51:59.012 --> 00:51:59.930
Pangako sa akin

00:52:01.681 --> 00:52:02.641
mananalo ka diyan.

00:52:20.700 --> 00:52:21.993
Sikat na mang-aawit na si Elijah

00:52:22.077 --> 00:52:24.704
